				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Even with no presence, this girl must have balls showing up somewhere crawling with the FS after breaking the law. It’s Misaki though, so I’m sure she’ll be fine.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"不过不论存在感再怎么薄弱，身为违反条例的人员，居然光明正大地跑到这种到处都是FS的场所──不，毕竟是美岬，或许真的不用担心吧。",
